口罩，防疫由每個人開始做起。<br />\n<br />\n民間人權陣線<br />\n2020年1月24日"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:03:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b164361f9b1b6d3a264ffce0ce3366d06b05f6e1","tid":1840200,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:03:46.000Z","msg":"今次香港人唔可以再任由醫護送死"},{"pid":"8c9f900c0fc6b6e46402fabbb80791cf79b7fd81","tid":1840200,"uid":248458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:05:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06825a5e2a297fea3f9f5afc60ea66a7f1348ab7","tid":1840200,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:07:11.000Z","msg":"希望佢哋盡快號召搞全民聲援活動"},{"pid":"0ab1c661751e1596adb9e8fa5af6bd7d3525d970","tid":1840200,"uid":296369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:13:29.000Z","msg":"有冇搞錯？唔比醫護戴N95....到時化咗人重大恐慌....."},{"pid":"7e699ea0bf1ad2898e6bb4509bf8e1dc8dbb7d2e","tid":1840200,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ab1c661751e1596adb9e8fa5af6bd7d3525d970","tid":1840200,"uid":296369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:13:29.000Z","msg":"有冇搞錯？唔比醫護戴N95....到時化咗人重大恐慌....."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:16:12.000Z","msg":"有乜做唔出"},{"pid":"39b62b8775e0e09241cafca96e9b958dd9bf8615","tid":1840200,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:16:55.000Z","msg":"我都全力支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2addff604439f51a40bc89de27fe54aaf2cd106a","tid":1840200,"uid":131188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:19:15.000Z","msg":"係咪戴左N95就唔俾返工呀? 咁快啲戴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41b45d22c601673df498802e057052281a365d1f","tid":1840200,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:20:40.000Z","msg":"全力支持醫護人員罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac5bc3c3f4ae0216091e886c3fda130e31bc8fcf","tid":1840200,"uid":266279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:20:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XzhtlQmMre4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXzhtlQmMre4&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZT8wxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=db2f8bbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XzhtlQmMre4</a><br />\n已經唔係嘔血咁簡單<br />\n實拍感染者病發無預兆直接倒地<br />\n沒有症狀，不發燒不咳嗽， 而是病發直接倒在地上死亡， 被人拖走"},{"pid":"a35256c5d09c33d525d4f36b0ad624451ba674d1","tid":1840200,"uid":3431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:24:29.000Z","msg":"仲諗緊罷唔罷嘅朋友 <br />\n唔該諗下自己親人 <br />\n佢地唔會想失去你<br />\n但你照返工幫人 <br />\n我尊重你 亦佩服你<br />\n但請寫定遺書 今次勁過03年"},{"pid":"dbcc143327ebe9f0fbedd77a141143ecbb39b756","tid":1840200,"uid":64609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:25:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3173794dd2803f9acf51970876b1545ccb99040f","tid":1840200,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:26:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"89d1ace3e84d22dfb19d5d4a40025362614fa88d","tid":1840200,"uid":64092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:41:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38ef113c244dd458bcee956eba1d804e9fe48e0e","tid":1840200,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06825a5e2a297fea3f9f5afc60ea66a7f1348ab7","tid":1840200,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:07:11.000Z","msg":"希望佢哋盡快號召搞全民聲援活動"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:44:36.000Z","msg":"立即遊行支持醫護罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5493c35d0e6efa64f8b74d0c5fc1668d7265623","tid":1840200,"uid":345689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:45:34.000Z",